cve_2025_54313_scavenger.description: Separate supply chain attack targeting eslint-config-prettier and related packages
cve_2025_54313_scavenger.phishing_vector: Spoofed NPM login page and typosquatted domain

malicious_code_patterns: AWS metadata endpoint IPv6 bracket notation
Common VCS token env vars possibly exfiltrated
GitHub App or Personal Access Token env vars
GitHub repo creation function name seen in payload
Shai-Hulud 2.0 destructive fallback wiping home directory
Shai-Hulud 2.0 preinstall hook pulling Bun payload
